AUDIO: 'We all know that. And it doesn\'t come with any storage uh when you order it, but I don\'t know if you can do pre-configurations or not. But yeah, so that\'s how it came for this review. Outside of that though, you do have UPS, uninterrupted power source. So, this is'

[01:26] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'kind of like a backup battery. So, if something goes out, a power outage goes out, you\'re not going to lose your data. You\'ve got that battery that\'s going to last you for a couple hours. You still can run it. It\'s kind of like a backup battery. You can run it off battery as'

