VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'well. It just takes about 100 watt power source. So, if you have a like a power brick that you use for your laptop or power bank, you just plug this in here. You\'re good to go with that as well. Um, it\'s relatively lightweight. I mean, the size of it is a bit bigger than I'

[01:50] [scene:talk]
